            <title>Math 121 Week 10 Activity</title>

        <objectives>
		<p>
            In this activity we will do the following:
        </p>
        <ul>
	  		<li>
	  			<p>
					Translate between rectangular graphs in the <m>r\theta</m>-plane to polar graphs in the <m>xy</m>-plane.
